---
title: Bacon and Mushroom Linguine with baby spinach and fresh chilli
description: The fresh chilli garnish is a wonderful complement to the salty meaty element of this dish. But fear not—the creamy cheesy sauce in this simple and satisfying recipe is a great way to cool down any heat you may be feeling.
